profile: My name is Leigh. I'm the owner and play a key role in the construction of every project. I also enjoy being part of the unique difference's in every job. Creating and beautifying like I'm leaving you pieces of my art. I'm very meticulous and have an eye like an eagle when it comes to grading(leveling). Throughout the years I've learned a lot of little tricks to the trade that only yrs of experience can produce. I also care about the final product. I know references and testimonials are key to building good customer relations to build my business. Though for myself as well, I'm always trying to achieve prefection in my trade. Its not just about the money for me. I take pride in creating a nice space for someone to enjoy. Doing what I do is very gratifying for me. Thanks, L ROC Construction.
